Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.10,0:00:29.19,Opening alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:24107,29195}{\blur3}On the stage, with the lights off…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.65,0:00:35.41,Opening alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:30656,35410}{\blur3}…blue shadows emerge.
