Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.55,0:02:05.89,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:120553,125892}Maya unexpectedly received the role of young Catherine at a "Wuthering Heights" audition, but she struggled to understand Catherine's strong love for Heathcliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.06,0:02:14.90,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:131064,134901}One day, she met Kazu, a young boy who is always alone and was starting to understand a way towards acting her role.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.05,0:02:27.10,Episode title,[title],0,0,0,,{TIME:141058,147105}{\an5\pos(766,750)\fscy95\blur1\fad(500,0)}—Episode 13—\NLove is Like a Mosaic
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.74,0:02:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:149749,149749}I'm off to practice!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.68,0:02:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:153687,153687}Practice?\NIt starts at one o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.74,0:02:55.74,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:175742,175742}Tōyō Theater Entrance\NAuthorized personnel only
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.11,0:02:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:178111,178111}Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.97,0:02:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:179979,179979}Morn–\NWhat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.61,0:03:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:182615,182615}What is she doing here so early?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.86,0:03:14.86,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:194861,194861}Tōyō Theater
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.54,0:03:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:210543,210543}I wonder what the president was thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.21,0:03:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:213213,213213}I know, betting on the possibilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.08,0:03:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:215081,215081}That Maya girl doesn't even have anything that shines about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.01,0:03:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:218018,218018}We can't even attempt to get any possibilities out of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.85,0:03:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:222856,222856}Well, I guess we just have to try.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.59,0:03:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:224591,224591}Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.69,0:03:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:229696,229696}– Then, I'll see you after practice.\N– Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.33,0:03:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:231331,231331}It's a great idea to have Egawa Yuki\Non stand-by, Mr. Sawaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.27,0:03:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:237270,237270}She's just right for Catherine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.77,0:03:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:239773,239773}I see. If Kitajima Maya doesn't do well, then…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.57,0:04:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:243576,243576}Yep, she'll surely make a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.12,0:04:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:258124,258124}Let's start the scene with young Catherine and Heathcliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.82,0:04:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:261828,261828}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.17,0:04:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:273173,273173}No, let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.94,0:04:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:274941,274941}Now that our father is dead,\NI'm the man of the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.17,0:04:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:278178,278178}Heathcliff will be treated\Nas a servant from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.71,0:04:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:280714,280714}Do you understand, Catherine?\NI won't allow you to play with a servant.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.51,0:04:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:283516,283516}No, let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.08,0:04:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:285085,285085}I won't stop being close to Heathcliff, no matter what you say!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.25,0:04:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:288254,288254}I love Heathcliff!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.25,0:04:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:290256,290256}Catherine!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.69,0:04:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:291691,291691}Don't go, Heathcliff!\NDon't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.02,0:04:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:294027,294027}Don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.32,0:04:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:296329,296329}{\i1}Don't go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.90,0:05:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:303903,303903}Heathcliff!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.02,0:05:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:321021,321021}Hmm, she's pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.98,0:05:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:322989,322989}We, as the adult team, can't underestimate the young ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.95,0:05:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:325959,325959}Hey, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.06,0:05:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:328061,328061}Ouch, she bit me for real!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.33,0:05:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:333333,333333}Hey, excuse me, guys, but enough of the love scenes. Pay attention to me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.70,0:05:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:337704,337704}Oh, what did I–
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.20,0:05:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:340206,340206}Look at this bite mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.91,0:05:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:343910,343910}Oh, I'm sorry, I…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.44,0:05:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:347447,347447}{\i1}What a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.48,0:05:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:349482,349482}{\i1}Her passion, her wildness,\NI was taken by her acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.42,0:05:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:355422,355422}I hope you'll like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.62,0:06:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:362629,362629}I knitted this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.86,0:06:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:363863,363863}It took me a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.56,0:06:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:365565,365565}You can wear this all the time,\Neven when I'm not around.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.43,0:06:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:368435,368435}Oh, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.17,0:06:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:373173,373173}I know you, Ryo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.37,0:06:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:375375,375375}That girl, Kitajima Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.47,0:06:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:377477,377477}She's the one who is on your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.17,0:06:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:379179,379179}I know so.\NI know everything about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.08,0:06:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:384084,384084}Well, Ryo, what's so attractive about her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.98,0:06:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:387987,387987}I'm prettier than she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.72,0:06:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:393727,393727}I'm a better actress than she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.06,0:06:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:398064,398064}It's just because the president had his eye on her that she got the role.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.10,0:06:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:402102,402102}She'll make a mistake soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.03,0:06:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:406039,406039}Then I'll play Catherine's role.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.14,0:06:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:409142,409142}That's what you promised me, too.\NHey, Ryo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.37,0:06:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:411378,411378}Why don't you shut up\Nfor a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.62,0:07:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:426626,426626}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.82,0:07:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:428828,428828}Sakurakōji!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.83,0:07:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:431831,431831}I stopped by your apartment, and they told me you were here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.86,0:07:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:433867,433867}Here, eat this before it gets cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.40,0:07:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:436403,436403}Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.07,0:07:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:442075,442075}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.41,0:07:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:443410,443410}This is delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.21,0:07:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:448215,448214}Gift{NOTE:御見舞}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.15,0:07:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:450150,450150}I'm impressed with your guts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.31,0:07:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:453319,453319}Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.68,0:07:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:454688,454688}To come and see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.29,0:07:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:457290,457290}I'm seriously concerned about your health, Miss Tsukikage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.19,0:07:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:461194,461194}As long as the play rights for "The Crimson Goddess" remain in my hands, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.87,0:07:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:470870,470870}Go ahead and take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.07,0:07:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:473073,473073}As cold and cruel as you are, I'm sure you have many ways, Mr. Masumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.01,0:07:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:479012,479012}I want it in a legitimate way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.51,0:08:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:483516,483516}I'll take it someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.72,0:08:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:495729,495729}You will play Catherine?\NThat's exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.49,0:08:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:498498,498498}I have an idea: why don't you read Heathcliff's words for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.26,0:08:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:503269,503269}It's hard to get the feel for it all by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.47,0:08:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:505472,505472}So I'll play your boyfriend?\NOf course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.41,0:08:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:514414,514414}They tell us that we can't play with each other, but we sneak out…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.15,0:08:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:522155,522155}…and finally here we are, Heathcliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.49,0:08:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:524491,524491}I hope my brother doesn't catch us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.89,0:08:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:527894,527894}W-We're fine. If he comes, then I'll hit him this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.43,0:08:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:532432,532432}Don't go anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.10,0:08:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:534100,534100}Stay by my side forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.07,0:08:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:537070,537070}Please stay with me forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.64,0:09:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:540640,540640}If you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.74,0:09:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:543743,543743}I am you, and you are me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.54,0:09:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:546546,546546}We are united as one soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.44,0:09:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:549449,549449}Promise me that we will stay the same when we're older.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.91,0:09:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:552919,552919}Your real father is an emperor of China, and your real mother is a queen of India.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.79,0:09:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:558792,558792}You'll leave here someday,\Nget rich, and come back to get me…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.89,0:09:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:563897,563897}{\i1}You are not looking at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.99,0:09:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:565999,565999}{\i1}The person in your eyes is not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.17,0:09:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:570170,570170}{\i1}The person you're in love with is Heathcliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.17,0:09:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:573173,573173}{\i1}I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.14,0:09:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:580146,580146}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.38,0:09:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:581381,581381}I… I'm not Heathcliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.61,0:09:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:583616,583616}I don't want to be\Na substitute or a shadow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.75,0:09:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:592759,592759}Sakurakōji, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.32,0:09:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:595328,595328}Why are you upset?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.81,0:10:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:612812,612812}Bidoro
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.01,0:10:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:617017,617017}Here, cheer up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.25,0:10:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:619252,619252}But, Sakurakōji was…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.95,0:10:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:622956,622956}You guys will be friends again soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.85,0:10:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:625859,625859}But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.89,0:10:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:627894,627894}How about sending him a ticket for the first play of "Wuthering Heights?"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.13,0:10:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:635135,635135}Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.40,0:10:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:637404,637404}You only need to concentrate on Catherine right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.97,0:10:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:640974,640974}To show Sakurakōji your wonderful Catherine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.61,0:10:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:644611,644611}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.97,0:10:45.97,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:645979,645979}Tōyō Theater
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.74,0:10:49.74,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:649749,649749}As the opening day approaches, the acting between Maya and Ryo, and Kagawa and Natsu intensifies.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.32,0:10:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:658324,658324}Catherine, we'll stay together forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.92,0:11:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:661928,661928}I am you, and you are me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.53,0:11:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:664531,664531}We are united as one soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.13,0:11:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:667133,667133}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.90,0:11:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:669903,669903}Mr. Majima's words sound so real lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.34,0:11:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:674341,674341}I wonder if they are in love in real life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.71,0:11:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:676710,676710}No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.41,0:11:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:678411,678411}Heathcliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.91,0:11:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:681915,681915}We'll be together forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.01,0:11:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:685018,685018}Forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.63,0:11:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:702635,702635}– Great work.\N– Good bye.\N– Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.11,0:11:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:714114,714114}Maya, let's walk home together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.15,0:11:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:717150,717150}C-Chilly…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.65,0:11:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:718651,718651}It is chilly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.12,0:12:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:720120,720120}Oh yeah, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.22,0:12:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:726226,726226}{\i1}That's my present!
Comment: 0,0:12:20.69,0:12:20.69,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:740698,740698}Eyecatch
Comment: 0,0:12:24.49,0:12:24.49,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:744493,744493}#Eyecatch
Comment: 0,0:12:27.45,0:12:27.45,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:747454,747454}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.14,0:12:28.14,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:748148,748148}Tōyō Theater
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.61,0:12:32.61,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:752619,752619}Today is the first day of "Wuthering Heights."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.76,0:12:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:765765,765765}Look at this hall.\NMy heart is beating so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.20,0:12:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:772205,772205}I wonder if Maya will be alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.60,0:12:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:774607,774607}She'll be fine. Once she's on the stage, she has so much courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.91,0:12:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:778912,778912}I'm kind of afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.98,0:13:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:783983,783983}{\i1}Catherine Arnshaw…\NNow I'll wear your mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.85,0:13:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:788855,788855}{\i1}We will be as one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.69,0:13:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:791691,791691}{\i1}Miss Tsukikage, Mr. Purple Rose,\NSakurakōji… please watch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.13,0:13:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:799132,799132}He's not here…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.66,0:13:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:800667,800667}What's wrong?\NLooking all around like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.37,0:13:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:803370,803370}That seat is reserved for Sakurakōji.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.07,0:13:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:807073,807073}Oh, Maya's boyfriend…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.60,0:13:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:809609,809609}The play is about to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.51,0:13:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:811511,811511}He'll show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.44,0:13:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:813446,813446}I hope so.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.55,0:13:44.55,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:824557,824557}There was the presence of Maya's rival, Himekawa Ayumi, and Yuki, who passionately loves Majima Ryo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.23,0:13:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:834234,834234}{\i1}Calm down.\NI'm Catherine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.43,0:13:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:837437,837437}{\i1}I love Heathcliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.57,0:13:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:839572,839572}{\i1}Just like Kazu, if Heathcliff is gone,\Nthen I'll be all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.07,0:14:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:844077,844077}{\i1}I don't want to be all alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.02,0:14:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:855021,855021}Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.69,0:14:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:861695,861695}{\i1}Let's do our best, Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.53,0:14:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:865532,865532}Get ready, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.14,0:14:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:880146,880146}What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.74,0:14:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:881748,881748}You want me to get along\Nwith Heathcliff?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.75,0:14:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:883750,883750}Hell no!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.83,0:14:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:897831,897831}You are so patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.60,0:15:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:900600,900600}Hmph, I'll kick him out of the Heights someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.07,0:15:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:908074,908074}Wearing my shoes, wearing my clothes… Who do you think you are!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.61,0:15:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:913613,913613}Don't!\NDon't, Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.81,0:15:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:915815,915815}Heathcliff has done nothing wrong!\NNothing wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.05,0:15:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:919052,919052}Get out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.35,0:15:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:920353,920353}What did you do to Catherine?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.93,0:15:36.93,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:936936,936936}With his passionate acting, the actor for Heandly has cut Majima Ryo's lip.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.54,0:15:43.54,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:943543,943543}This accident was about to cause a problem for the flow of the play.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.48,0:15:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:949482,949482}{\i1}I have to do something.\NI have to help Heathcliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.98,0:15:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:951985,951985}{\i1}What would Heathcliff do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.45,0:15:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:955455,955455}{\i1}What would Catherine do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.43,0:16:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:968435,968435}You are so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.07,0:16:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:970070,970070}You are bleeding like this, and you don't even complain about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.47,0:16:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:973473,973473}I love that about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.91,0:16:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:977911,977911}{\i1}Maya…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.35,0:16:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:983350,983350}Let's go, Heathcliff!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.51,0:16:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:985518,985518}Try to catch me. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.55,0:16:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:987554,987554}Come on, hurry!\NTry to catch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.99,0:16:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:992992,992992}Catherine, you are the only person I love in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.39,0:16:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:996396,996396}You love me,\Nmy everything, my soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.96,0:16:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1000967,1000967}What were you thinking to rip your clothes off!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.23,0:16:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1004237,1004237}Catherine!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.24,0:16:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1009242,1009242}{\i1}That kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.77,0:16:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1010777,1010777}{\i1}To be able to do that in a blink of an eye, you must love Majima.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.68,0:16:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1014681,1014681}Here, hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.04,0:16:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1016049,1016049}I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.41,0:17:04.25,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:1019419,1024257}Despite the feelings of Yuki and Sakurakōji, who don't want to believe Maya and Ryo are in love, the love between Heathcliff and Catherine was getting more and more passionate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.06,0:17:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1029062,1029062}Heathcliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.60,0:17:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1039606,1039606}Those two.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.90,0:17:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1040907,1040907}I hope they didn't forget their words.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.84,0:17:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1043843,1043843}Look at them: silent for so long, but still maintaining the audience's attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.91,0:17:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1048915,1048915}What a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.01,0:17:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1051017,1051017}– Now, let's go together.\N– Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.26,0:17:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1060260,1060260}We finally ran away, Heathcliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.62,0:17:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1062629,1062629}I hope my brother doesn't find us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.56,0:17:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1064564,1064564}We'll be fine. If he comes after us, then I'll hit him this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.26,0:17:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1068268,1068268}Don't go anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.37,0:17:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1071371,1071371}Those eyes…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.44,0:17:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1073440,1073440}You are me, and I am you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.40,0:17:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1075408,1075408}We are united as one soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.87,0:17:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1077877,1077877}Promise me that we won't change when we grow up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.08,0:18:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1081081,1081081}Yes, Heathcliff!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.75,0:18:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1084751,1084751}– Mr. Hayami.\N– Let's go outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.82,0:18:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1092826,1092826}If you love her, then watch her till the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.49,0:18:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1097497,1097497}I love her. That's why I don't want to watch it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.80,0:18:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1100800,1100800}Go back to your seat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.30,0:18:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1102302,1102302}You, you'll never understand how I feel!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.77,0:18:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1105772,1105772}Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.74,0:18:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1110744,1110744}As long as you live here, I'll stay here in the Heights.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.34,0:18:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1114347,1114347}I'll put up with anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.68,0:18:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1118685,1118685}Heathcliff, we'll be together forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.79,0:18:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1132799,1132799}It's our turn now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.63,0:18:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1136636,1136636}Kind of awkward to go out now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.30,0:18:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1138304,1138304}We have much more of a career and longer scenes, but I don't feel so confident.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.40,0:19:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1142409,1142409}Come on, we're the main roles here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.71,0:19:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1144711,1144711}We are not going to let her take the play.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.01,0:19:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1145011,1145011}Dressing room
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.98,0:19:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1155989,1155989}I wonder if Sakurakōji was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.06,0:19:28.26,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:1163063,1168268}The combination between Natsu Eriko and Kagawa Hideaki was just as attractive, and the first night of "Wuthering Heights" ended in success.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.08,0:19:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1189089,1189089}{\i1}Sakurakōji, I told him to wait here in the letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.23,0:19:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1199232,1199232}Are you looking for Heathcliff, Catherine?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.47,0:20:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1203470,1203470}You did really well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.14,0:20:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1207140,1207140}Passionate and wild Catherine…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.44,0:20:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1210443,1210443}…yes, that was true…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.91,0:20:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1217917,1217917}…but, it was sort of like a little child\Nwhose toy was taken away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.78,0:20:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1221788,1221788}Not the kind of passionate love for a lover.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.82,0:20:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1226826,1226826}{\i1}Not a passionate love for a lover?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.73,0:20:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1232732,1232732}Seems like you have much more to learn in acting out love, little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.40,0:20:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1239406,1239406}Hurry up and grow up, little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.20,0:20:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1243209,1243209}My name is not "little girl!"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.62,0:20:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1254621,1254621}Huh…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.55,0:20:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1256556,1256556}How was Kitajima Maya?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.85,0:20:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1258858,1258858}Was she playing Catherine in love well?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.49,0:21:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1262495,1262495}She doesn't know real love yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.10,0:21:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1268101,1268101}Mr. Majima was so great!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.50,0:21:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1270503,1270503}I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.50,0:21:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1276509,1276509}Hey, Maya. I'll take you home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.11,0:21:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1281114,1281114}Ryo…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.31,0:21:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1283316,1283316}I was waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.45,0:21:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1285452,1285452}You can give me a ride home, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.30,0:21:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1307307,1307307}Kitajima Maya, Kitajima Maya.\NThere's a phone call for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.94,0:21:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1310944,1310944}Oh, that might be Sakurakōji!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.18,0:21:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1315181,1315181}Hi, this is Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.61,0:21:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1316616,1316616}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.85,0:21:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1319853,1319853}What are you saying, Rei?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.42,0:22:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1322422,1322422}You're not serious, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.79,0:22:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1325792,1325792}{\i1}Miss Tsukikage is at her last breath?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.96,0:22:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1327961,1327961}{\i1}Don't die! Please, don't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.74,0:22:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1346746,1346746}{\i1}You promised me that you won't be able to die till you direct "The Crimson Goddess."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.64,0:22:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1348648,1348648}{\i1}Please don't die, Teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.61,0:22:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1350617,1350617}{\i1}Don't give in to the illness.\NDon't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.98,0:22:32.98,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:1352986,1352986}Operating room in use
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.72,0:22:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1361728,1361728}{\i1}No… No!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.76,0:22:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1363763,1363763}{\i1}Don't die!\NTeacher!
Comment: 0,0:22:51.37,0:22:51.37,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:1371370,1371370}Ending
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.62,0:23:04.75,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1378624,1384754}{\blur3}It is lonely by myself…
